headline: Did Walmart's (WMT) New Healthcare and Logistics Moves Just Shift Its Investment Narrative?
summary: Walmart recently expanded its health and wellness offerings by partnering with Eli Lilly to provide direct-to-consumer access for the weight-loss drug Zepbound in its pharmacies, while also integrating GOFO's nationwide logistics services to strengthen its e-commerce marketplace delivery capabilities. These collaborations underscore Walmart’s drive to enhance healthcare access and delivery efficiency, reflecting a multi-faceted approach to digital transformation and marketplace...
